OL,3,CCrane driver who rescued worker from
OL,4,Cburning building awarded medal
OL,6,FA crane driver who saved a fellow
OL,7,Fworker from a burning building in
OL,8,FReading in Berkshire has been honoured
OL,9,Fby the British Fire Services
OL,10,FAssociation.
OL,12,FGlen Edwards has been described as a
OL,13,Fhero for which took place when a tower
OL,14,Fblock caught fire at the Station Hill
OL,15,Fdevelopment in the town centre at
OL,16,F11.30am on Thursday 23 November.
OL,18,FHe used his skills as a crane
OL,19,Foperator, to lower a cage onto the
OL,20,Froof of the high rise block, while
OL,21,Fflames and smoke engulfed the area.
