OL,6,FThe worker was able to climb inside
OL,7,Fthe cage, and was then winched to
OL,8,Fsafety.
OL,10,FOn Monday (8 April) The British Fire
OL,11,FServices Association (BFSA) presented
OL,12,FGlen Edwards with the Commendation
OL,13,FMedal.
OL,15,FPosting on their Facebook page, a BFSA
OL,16,Fspokesperson said: The BFSA were
OL,17,Fpleased to present the Commendation
OL,18,FMedal to Glen Edwards who was the
OL,19,FCrane Operator involved in the rescue
OL,20,Fof a worker from a roof-top fire in
OL,21,FReading last year."
