OL,6,FMembers of the public were quick to
OL,7,Fcongratulate Edwards.
OL,9,FOne Facebook user posted:
OL,10,F"Congratulations from a fellow
OL,11,Frecipient!".
OL,13,FWhile another person wrote: "Awesome
OL,14,Fjob!"
OL,16,FMore than 50 firefighters were sent to
OL,17,Ftackle the blaze at the Station Hill
OL,18,Fdevelopment.
