OL,6,FHundreds of construction workers and
OL,7,Foffice staff were evacuated from
OL,8,Fsurrounding buildings as fire crews
OL,9,Fworked to contain the fire, which
OL,10,Fspread to the top of a high-rise tower
OL,11,Funder construction near the train
OL,12,Fstation.
OL,14,FGlen, a crane operator of 30 years,
OL,15,Fsaid it had "not been your average day
OL,16,Fat work".
OL,18,FHe said: "I was driving the crane at
OL,19,Fthe time. I saw someone waving his
OL,20,Fcoat. I got a radio call to get the
OL,21,Fman riser.
